# Classroom upload safety

- Confirm the source file path and file type before renaming.
- Preserve the original file extension when changing names.
- Use deterministic naming format: `<course>-<assignment>-<student>-<date>`.
- Never expose OAuth secrets, tokens, or private links in logs.
- Before upload, verify target Classroom course and assignment identifiers.
